      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/1/9",
      "text": [
        ": قال أبو عبد الله: أما واللهِ لو كانتْ على أفواهِكم أوكِيَةً لحدَّثتُ كُلَّ امرئٍ منكُم بما لهُ، واللهِ لَو وَجَدتُ أتقِياءَ لتَكَلّمتُ، واللهُ المُستَعانُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(9) The previous series from al-Hasan from Karram al-Khath’ami that Abu Abdullah (as) had said: “By Allah, if your mouths were bound with bands, I would tell every one of you something. By Allah, if I found (atqiya’) among you, I would talk. Allah is the Assistant!”"
        ]
      }
    },
